CSRMESH_TUNING_ACK_CONFIG_T Struct Reference
CSRmesh&trade; » Models » Tuning Model

Current tuning config for a device: This message comes as a response to a SET_CONFIG. Encoding its various fields follow the same convention as the ones exposed in SET_CONFIG.
